{"title":"为歌唱列宁诞辰纪念作——歌词二首","authors":["田间"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":4,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"为歌唱列宁诞辰纪念作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——歌词二首\t田间\t一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伏尔加波涛滚滚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"列宁在风暴中诞生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像海燕冲进怒涛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像雄鹰展翅飞腾——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"列宁和阶级弟兄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打开世界第一个黎明。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马克思的继承者，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是伟大的列宁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他用革命的火种，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唤起被压迫的人们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要粉碎旧世界的锁链，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把新世界早日建成。\t二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宇宙像一叶扁舟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"列宁是一位舵手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗就是船上帆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿过四洋五大洲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旧世界已经崩溃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新世界担在我们肩头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地球、月球、星球，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟着工人阶级走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"列宁和我们一起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"登上第一座港口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他和我们永别时说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要继续前进别停留！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新世界的主人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是我们劳动人民。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切暴君的王座，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正在纷纷崩溃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帝国主义的末日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不久也就要来临。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想的光辉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照耀着我们人民公社，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高举马列主义的战旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全世界无产者联合起来！（附图片）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"列宁（木刻）黄永玉"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}